com.aylanetworks.agilelink

类 MenuHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aylanetworks.agilelink.MenuHandler

  • public class MenuHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    The MenuHandler class is a static helper class used to process menu events. This class will perform the necessary operations for menu items from the Settings menu or navigation drawer menu.
